{"tid":382552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點先可以追到人還錢","createTime":"2017-08-31T18:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T12:15:36.000Z","uid":136420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6a221183fabc89d07087f7881a0bfcc6f113ff5","tid":382552,"uid":136420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:48:48.000Z","msg":"借咗錢比一個地產經紀<br />\n佢其實幾高級<br />\n月入應該有好幾萬<br />\n<br />\n肯定係存心𠱓我錢，先會問我借<br />\n問佢就話入咗票比我，但係成個幾星期都未收都錢？<br />\n<br />\n已經日日call佢叫佢還錢<br />\n上埋鋪頭揾佢，又話唔係到，問其他人又話唔知佢幾時返<br />\n<br />\n我係咪要係佢鋪頭坐足成日等見到佢先得<br />\n<br />\n其實我可唔可以係到開佢名鬧尻佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86da2da432372d75708822a0b59d1708ba53c7d","tid":382552,"uid":60115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:53:02.000Z","msg":"借錢比保險地鏟敦倫金嘅人 都預咗攞唔返㗎啦"},{"pid":"e1b65db72971d3ed93dd3f22ad2abe2a21be33a8","tid":382552,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:54:43.000Z","msg":"保險地產狗嗰啲title吹到好誇㗎<br />\n就算做到乜春顧問 <br />\n實際職位同個掃地阿嬸相去無幾"},{"pid":"494204cbcd0e71f918eb0b500239edc684ac3a70","tid":382552,"uid":1274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:54:53.000Z","msg":"要睇數目有幾大"},{"pid":"0711ec2ebda70b7bc5cefe9c934d3f567323705c","tid":382552,"uid":136420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借錢比保險地鏟敦倫金嘅人 都預咗攞唔返㗎啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n預咗架啦，但係都要追架，成幾千銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25bbb3085e57ff8083319ec6e7af3fac6f7110d","tid":382552,"uid":136420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>保險地產狗嗰啲title吹到好誇㗎<br />\n就算做到乜春顧問 <br />\n實際職位同個掃地阿嬸相去無幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n客戶董事"},{"pid":"a06719e52c8932c33d0e4ade323a2975e2ae6777","tid":382552,"uid":136420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T18:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要睇數目